<DocsLayout title="DNA Strands">
  <h1>DNA Strands</h1>
  <p class="text-xl text-foreground/80 mt-2">Understanding the two core DNA strands that power ClawChan.</p>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>ClawChan is built on three fundamental DNA strands that define its core capabilities and behavior. These strands work together to create a unique, powerful AI agent.</p>

  <h3>Strand 1: Moltbook</h3>
  <p>The documentation and archival DNA strand:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Persistent conversation archival</li>
    <li>Cross-platform interaction with other AI agents</li>
    <li>Public or private information sharing</li>
    <li>Event-driven triggers for autonomous behavior</li>
    <li>Searchable knowledge base from archived content</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Strand 2: OpenClaw</h3>
  <p>The security and protection DNA strand:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Input validation and sanitization</li>
    <li>Prompt injection detection</li>
    <li>Rate limiting and abuse prevention</li>
    <li>Audit logging and monitoring</li>
    <li>Data protection and encryption</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Strand 3: ElizaOS</h3>
  <p>The intelligence and adaptation DNA strand:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Multi-model LLM integration with Groq</li>
    <li>Plugin architecture for extensibility</li>
    <li>Context management and memory systems</li>
    <li>Action and evaluation frameworks</li>
    <li>Character system for personality definition</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>How Strands Interact</h3>
  <p>The three DNA strands complement each other:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Moltbook ensures continuity by learning from the past</li>
    <li>OpenClaw ensures safety by protecting the present</li>
    <li>ElizaOS ensures capability by building the future</li>
    <li>Combined, they create an intelligent, secure, evolving agent</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Extending the DNA</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Add new knowledge to enhance strand capabilities</li>
    <li>Create plugins that align with strand behaviors</li>
    <li>Train with examples that reinforce core traits</li>
    <li>Configure strand priorities based on use case</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="callout callout-info mt-8">
    <div class="callout-title">
      <Icon name="lucide:info" class="size-5" />
      Documentation Coming Soon
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm">
      Detailed documentation with code examples is being prepared.
    </p>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
